No. 10-8159 (R46-017). Eric Hanson, Petitioner v. Illinois. 563 U.S. 931, 131 S. Ct. 2091,

179 L. Ed. 2d 798,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2822. April 13, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Illinois in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.
